Description: OAuth2/OIDC SASL plugin for Cyrus SASL
 This package provides an OAuth2/OIDC authentication mechanism plugin
 for Cyrus SASL. It allows applications using SASL to authenticate
 users via OAuth2/OpenID Connect providers.
 .
 The plugin supports:
  - OAuth2 Bearer token authentication
  - OpenID Connect ID token validation
  - JWT token introspection
  - Multiple issuer support
  - Configurable audience validation
 .
 This is particularly useful for modern email servers like Cyrus IMAP
 that need to integrate with OAuth2 identity providers.
